<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="31Mar1925"><font color="red">31 March 1925</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver, typed): Many thanks for the copy of the New Republic with Mr. Muir&apos;s interesting article &hellip; When is [Miss Marsden&apos;s] book to be published, for I gather from your letter that it is not finished? &hellip; The second semi-attack has removed all print out of my field of vision &hellip; I cannot send the Criterion piece to be typed yet </div>
